    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3>Instructions</h3>

<p>Download the file below to a folder on your computer. I suggest a new
folder inside whatever folder you are already using for this
class.</p>

<p>You will need to create a CSS file called &ldquo;style.css&rdquo;. There are 5
mandatory tasks and 3 optional tasks specified in the HTML. You should
generally be able to complete the assignment without editing the HTML
at all (just write CSS).</p>

<p>This assignment is due on Thursday.</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span> (selectors_challenge.html)</span> <a href='https://mkornblum.github.io/de271-fa14/downloads/code/selectors_challenge.html'>download</a></figcaption>
